metadata.name: "Feu" a Nexus-8 Replicant
metadata.description:
Built for Off-World warfare. 

She will NOT be retired. 

The Replicants is a series of photographic prints of AI in human form. These machines are so advanced that they think they are human.

They have graced Modern Vintage Photography with their being in the studio and on location.

Their images have been hand printed using an archival, Prussian blue, 1842 printing method called Cyanotype.

The original collector of these images is entitled to the physical 1/1 print, or a second video NFT of the Replicant (physical print) being destroyed by fire.
